            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Notarized build — no more Gatekeeper warnings</li>
                    <li>Project-level settings editing with override toggles</li>
